  <brief_title>Qualitative Pain Measurement at Patients With Degenerative Low Back Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Qualitative Pain Measurement and Sensitization at Patients With Degenerative Low Back Pain With Indication for Lumbar Intervertebral Disc</official_title>
